ðŸŒŒ AURORA STYLE GUIDE
================================================================================

VISUAL LANGUAGE:
- **Form**: Ethereal, soft, dreamlike with flowing gradients
- **Colors**: Cool purples, pinks, blues like northern lights (#a78bfa, #ec4899, #06b6d4), soft pastels
- **Typography**: Elegant sans-serif (Inter, Plus Jakarta Sans) with light weights for body, semi-bold for headings
- **Shapes**: Soft rounded corners (large radius), organic blob shapes, flowing curves
- **Interaction**: Gentle fade transitions, floating animations, color shift on hover

DESIGN TOKENS GUIDANCE:
- Background: Soft gradient (purpleâ†’blueâ†’pink) or muted dark with colorful overlay
- Primary: Purple/pink (#a78bfa, #ec4899) with soft glow
- Surface: Frosted glass cards with gradient borders
- Radius: 1rem - 1.5rem (large rounded, almost pill)
- Shadow: Soft, colorful shadows (purple/pink tint)
- Animation: 400-800ms gentle easing, floating/drifting motions

COMPONENT PATTERNS:
- Buttons: Soft gradients, gentle glow, floating hover effect
- Cards: Translucent with gradient borders, backdrop blur, subtle color shifts
- Inputs: Light borders with gradient on focus, soft inner shadow
- Text: Gradient text with aurora colors, gentle letter-spacing

LAYOUT & SPACING:
- Flowing, organic layouts with asymmetry
- Large breathing room (py-16, py-32)
- Centered content with soft edges
- Background: Abstract gradient blobs, aurora-like light streams

ATMOSPHERE:
- Magical, serene, otherworldly
- Soft lighting with colorful ambient glow
- Dreamlike quality through blur and gradients
- Gentle motion evokes calm and wonder

DO NOT:
- Use harsh contrasts or neon intensity
- Create rigid, geometric layouts
- Use monochrome or single-color schemes
- Apply aggressive animations

================================================================================

